### List analysis pricing
GET {{baseUrl}}/analysis_pricing
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create analysis pricing
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis_pricing
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "analysis_type": "Gar Purity",
  "description": "Standard Gas Purity analysis",
  "standard_rate": "100.00",
  "rushed_rate": "150.00",
  "sample_fee": "25.00",
  "active": true
}

### Get analysis pricing by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/analysis_pricing/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update analysis pricing
PUT {{baseUrl}}/analysis_pricing/2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description",
  "standard_rate": "110.00",
  "rushed_rate": "160.00",
  "sample_fee": "30.00",
  "active": true
}

### Delete analysis pricing
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/analysis_pricing/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
